  "title": "Loan Officer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Title:</strong> Loan Officer<br>\n <strong>Location:</strong> Chinatown<br>\n <strong>Employment Type:</strong> Full-Time</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>About Our Client:</strong><br>\nOur client is a reputable financial institution known for responsible lending and professional service. They value stable, committed team members who build lasting client relationships.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Description:</strong><br>\nOur client is seeking an experienced Loan Officer from licensed moneylenders. You will assess loan applications, advise clients on suitable products, ensure regulatory compliance, and maintain strong client relationships.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Evaluate and process loan applications accurately</li>\n  <li>Advise clients on appropriate loan solutions</li>\n  <li>Ensure compliance with regulations and internal policies</li>\n  <li>Monitor repayments and manage overdue accounts</li>\n  <li>Maintain strong client relationships</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Experience as a Loan Officer or similar role in a licensed moneylender</li>\n  <li>Strong credit assessment and risk management skills</li>\n  <li>Excellent communication and interpersonal abilities</li>\n  <li>Preference for candidates with stable employment history</li>\n  <li>Finance or banking qualifications are a plus</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>What Our Client Offers:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Competitive salary with performance-based incentives</li>\n  <li>Opportunities for growth within a stable institution</li>\n  <li>Supportive work environment with training and development</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>How to Apply:</strong><br>\nSubmit your resume and a brief cover letter highlighting your licensed moneylender experience or just click apply and we will reach out to you.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>WeCruit Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0270</p>\n<p>EA Personnel: Tan Soon Hock (Steven) | Registration No. R1109889</p>",
